text: Alejandra Amalia Sepúlveda Orbenes (born 13 November 1965) is a politician currently serving as a member of the Chamber of Deputies of Chile, representing District 16 of the O'Higgins Region. She previously served as President of the Chamber of Deputies. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:People from Viña del Mar Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies of Chile Category:Presidents of the Chamber of Deputies of Chile Category:Austral University of Chile alumni
